/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high vantage point, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street is flanked by tall buildings, their gray and brown facades standing in stark contrast to the overcast sky above. A few trees punctuate the urban landscape, their green foliage adding a touch of nature to the cityscape. Cars of various colors are parked along the sides of the street, hinting at the daily life and activity in this part of the city. The street itself is lined with yellow traffic cones, guiding the flow of vehicles and adding a pop of color to the scene. Despite the overcast sky, the image paints a vivid picture of a day in the life of Beijing.
